				\begin{document}$${{\it{B}}_ \bot }$$\end{document} at the selected site (Fig. 4b, lower panel and Supplementary Discussion 2). The measured 15N Larmor frequency as a function of the varying transverse field B⊥\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
